### PacBio® DevNet
PacBio DevNet is the central resource for life scientists, informatics researchers and independent software vendors to learn about SMRT® sequencing technology, share ideas and code, and communicate with each other.

Datasets, source code, application programming interfaces, and documentation are shared and distributed throughout the site.

tagline: The DevNet project on github stores the PacBio® DevNet website pages.
